            "extra_id": 0x42,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x0,
            "msg_string": "Sophie! Plachta! Are you home?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2a,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Wah, Leon. What's wrong?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x8,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0x43,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "Nothing's wrong. I finished Plachta's clothes, so I brought them over."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x8,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0x44,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x3,
            "msg_string": "Here you go."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x17,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x4,
            "msg_string": "Wow..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x116,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x5,
            "msg_string": "This is..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x8,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x6,
            "msg_string": "What do you think? I emphasized ease of mobility, but I also made it feminine."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x18,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x7,
            "msg_string": "Leon...! These clothes are amazing!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x116,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x8,
            "msg_string": "Yes. I didn't even imagine that it would be to this degree of perfection."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x8,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x9,
            "msg_string": "Sounds like you like it, that's good."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x19,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0xa,
            "msg_string": "Yeah, I really like it! Right, Plachta?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x116,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0xb,
            "msg_string": "Yes, they're... Quite to my liking."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x8,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0x5,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xc,
            "msg_string": "That's good. Anyway, I should get going."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x8,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0x2b,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0xd,
            "msg_string": "I want to see you wearing those clothes real soon, got it? Promise me."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3c,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xe,
            "msg_string": "Yes, we promise. Thank you so much!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x8,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0x2d,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xf,
            "msg_string": "Hehe. See you later."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x30,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x10,
            "msg_string": "Leon really is amazing... She was able to make such lovely clothes..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x116,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x11,
            "msg_string": "Yes, she possesses quite a level of skill... She's obviously not ordinary, even from my point of view."
